# Required: your OpenAI API key
OPENAI_API_KEY=sk-...

# Optional: change the port (default 8787)
# PORT=8787

# --- Swap provider ---
# To use a different model provider, replace @ai-sdk/openai with the
# corresponding AI SDK adapter (e.g. @ai-sdk/anthropic, @ai-sdk/google)
# and update the import + openai() call in src/index.ts accordingly.
# The AIModel wrapper is provider-agnostic — only the LanguageModel instance changes.
